<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <title>Preferred Answer Congratulation</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.5;
      color: #333;
    }
    h1 {
      font-size: 24px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    p {
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #f5f5f5;
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 20px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #999;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Congratulations!</h1>
    <p>Hi <%= user.name %>,</p>
    <p>Your answer on <%= question.title %> has been marked as the preferred answer.</p>
    <p>We appreciate your contribution to the community and we hope that you will continue to share your knowledge and insights with us.</p>
    <p>If you have any questions or feedback, please feel free to contact us at <%= support.email %>.</p>
    <p>Thank you for being a valuable member of our community.</p>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>This email was sent to <%= user.email %> as part of your <%= app.name %> account.</p>
      <p>Please do not reply to this email.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
